pullRequest.title: Update READMEs for doc building changes
pullRequest.bodyText:
Explicitly call out how to skip doc builds for companies who cannot use Docker, and how to run them without Docker separately.
Remove Known issues, as they are no longer issues
Remove deprecated sphinx autobuild
